1.0.1.name: wordpress/heypublisher-submission-manager
1.0.1.description:
About HeyPublisher Submission Manager

This plugin allows publishers and blog owners to accept unsolicited submissions from unregistered users. You no longer have to create accounts for each and every writer in your system who wants to submit content to you for consideration. Instead, submissions to your website are handled by the HeyPublisher.com web-service via this plugin.

You define the type of writing you want to receive. You control the flow of unsolicited content coming into your publication. You have more time to run your publication.

Think of us as a "digital slush pile" for your website.

Use of this plugin allows you to quickly and easily preview submissions, mark submissions for 'review', accept submissions for publication, or reject submissions, removing them from your slush pile. All acceptance/rejection communications with
